column5: Second round was no less than 62 wings. Some guy ate 66 wings in 14 mins.  http://news.yahoo.com/nphotos/Wing-Bowl/ss...r2075993469.jpg The Winner  http://news.yahoo.com/nphotos/Wing-Bowl/ss...4ba5fa193b5a344 Fans in the Stands  http://images.search.yahoo.com/search/imag...16&ei=UTF-8 Best Entourage  http://images.search.yahoo.com/search/imag...p;ni=20&b=1 More Pictures
Was wondering what PF Steve was doing last week....

LOL Rap, really how many people could lift and chew that many wings in so short a time! Not to mention the wash! Had to be beer involved! Dang  Did I cover all the bases? Beer, wings. dang? Check! Ohio out!

There are other eating events but the WING BOWL is the main event. Here is the list for the others including PRIZE$. It might be for you next year?  http://philadelphia.about.com/od/calendaro...ng_bowl_15a.htm
